  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libmbim</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libmbim</application> is a glib-based library for talking to WWAN modems 
      and devices which speak the Mobile Interface Broadband Model (MBIM) protocol.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

